      "level": 1,
      "text": "TIMING BELT"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "CAUTION:\na. Do not bend or twist timing belt.\nb. After removing timing belt, do not turn crankshaft and camshaft separately because valves will strike piston heads.\nc. Ensure that timing belt, camshaft sprocket, crankshaft sprocket, injection pump sprocket and belt tensioner are clean and free from oil and water.",
      "style": "caution"
    },
